reviewText:
Yes, I am a fan of hers.  Yes, I bought it for her.  I thought this was going to be porn stars dancing, stripping, talking.  Instead, it's hardcore scenes of 6 different stars.
Kaci Starr, Kendra Secrets, Kathleen, Jordan James, Katie Morgan & Vanessa Lane.
Kaci's scene was cut short, Kendra goes wild, Kathleen is a lithe & enthusiastic performer, Jordan was lame in comparison, Katie was fantastic & Vanessa kept going but was nice.
